Academy of Music.

00:02:36.210 --> 00:02:39.900
Lehtonen's been a soloist with the
Helsinki City Orchestra as well

00:02:39.900 --> 00:02:43.630
as the Aalborg and Odense
Symphony Orchestras among others.

00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:46.390 position:56%
In 2007, he received a special award

00:02:46.390 --> 00:02:50.860
at the XI Concorso Violino
Citta di Brescia Competition.

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:56.110
His sound recordings include Haydn,
Kuchler, Segestrom and Kreisler.

